        {
          "title": "Verify listview query limits and pagination behavior",
          "description": "Ensures performance and user experience when dealing with large datasets.\n\nTest Steps:\n\n1. Navigate to an object's listview (e.g., Email Logs) which contains more records than the defined query limit (e.g., >500 records).\n   Expected: Only the first page of records (up to the query limit) is initially displayed. UI controls for pagination or loading more records are present.\n\n2. Interact with pagination controls (e.g., click 'Next Page' or 'Load More').\n   Expected: Subsequent sets of records are loaded and displayed, up to the maximum fetch limit or end of data.",
          "priority": "Medium",
