        {
          "title": "Verify 'View All' permission behavior in listview",
          "description": "Crucial for access control; ensures users with 'View All' see all records, while others see only accessible ones.\n\nTest Steps:\n\n1. As a user with only 'read' permission (no 'view_all') for an object, navigate to its listview.\n   Expected: Only records that the user owns or has inherited access to are displayed.\n\n2. As a user with 'view_all' permission for the same object, navigate to its listview.\n   Expected: All records for the object are displayed, regardless of ownership.",
