        {
          "title": "Verify default Email Logs listview display and sorting",
          "description": "Ensures the basic listview functionality loads correctly with predefined settings.\n\nTest Steps:\n\n1. Navigate to the Email Logs section in the Admin application.\n   Expected: The 'All Email Logs' listview loads with columns: 'logged_at', 'delivery_status', 'subject', 'to_addresses', 'source_record_name', 'actor_label'. Records are sorted by 'Logged At' in descending order.",
