        {
          "title": "Login to Admin and verify dashboard loads",
          "description": "Ensures that valid admin credentials allow access to the admin console and the main dashboard is displayed.\n\nTest Steps:\n\n1. Navigate to https://ops.acchindra.com/admin\n   Expected: Login page is displayed with username and password fields.\n\n2. Enter username/email \"adminacc\" and password \"adminacc@2026\"\n   Expected: Credentials are filled in the respective fields.\n\n3. Click the \"Sign In\" button\n   Expected: User is authenticated and redirected to https://ops.acchindra.com/admin/?nav=apps&appId=app21vhj4w.\n\n4. Verify that the top navigation bar and sidebar are visible\n   Expected: Topbar and sidebar elements are present, indicating dashboard loaded.\n\n5. Assert that no error toast or alert is shown\n   Expected: No error messages appear.",
