              {
                "title": "Admin shared list view controls are available in reachable Apps context",
                "description": "Admin shared list view controls are available in reachable Apps context\n\nTest Steps:\n\n1. Navigate to https://ops.acchindra.com/admin and log in if prompted by entering username/email \"adminacc\" and password \"adminacc@2026\", then click the sign-in/login control.\n   Expected: Admin session is established successfully.\n\n2. Continue to the inspected target context by opening or verifying https://ops.acchindra.com/admin/?nav=apps&appId=app21vhj4w.\n   Expected: The Admin Apps context is loaded for the selected app scope.\n\n3. Verify a list view or table/grid container is displayed for the Admin Apps context; if no list is visible because inspection is blocked, capture that as the next required verification point.\n   Expected: The test identifies the Apps list view container, or documents that the reachable page requires manual/automation follow-up because no visible list metadata was available from inspection.\n\n4. Verify the common list view toolbar controls that are visible in this context, prioritizing New, Refresh, Export CSV, Export PDF, Summary, Settings, search box, and list-view selector where present.\n   Expected: Visible controls are enabled or disabled according to access, and no unrelated admin page or unverified menu name is assumed.\n\n5. Verify the list body shows either headers and rows, or a clear empty-state if no Apps records are available.\n   Expected: The list provides a deterministic data state: populated rows with headers, or an empty-state message; it is not blank without explanation.\n\n6. Use the visible search control, if present, to enter a short query and then clear it.\n   Expected: The list view remains stable, refreshes/filter results appropriately, and returns to its original state after clearing the query without errors.\n\n7. Click Refresh if visible.\n   Expected: The list reloads and returns to a completed state with headers plus rows or empty-state, with no persistent loading or applica